nodes.text: Hi Dr Person1, I was in the ER on MM/DD/YYYY for belly pain and Person2  PA-C in Extended care clinic. He prescribed me Ketorolac (Toradol) and my insurance would not cover it. I am willing to pay for it out of pocket. Can u call it into Org, Location please. It takes the stomach pain away and it seems to happen like once every 3 months so I don have to drive an hour to ER for them to tell me it from the Cancer
